WEBVTT

00:07.204 --> 00:09.039
There it is.

00:09.041 --> 00:10.541
Valencia.

00:10.543 --> 00:12.077
How do you think this should go down?

00:12.078 --> 00:15.078
Do you think I should save the kingdom
and then rescue Madalena?

00:15.080 --> 00:16.647
Or do you think
I should rescue, then save?

00:16.648 --> 00:19.750
'Cause I just want it to have
a dramatic build, you know?

00:19.751 --> 00:21.385
I mean, either way,

00:21.386 --> 00:23.120
we're all gonna live happily ever after.

00:23.121 --> 00:24.488
Yep.

00:24.489 --> 00:25.823
I'm sure that's exactly how
it's going to be.

00:25.824 --> 00:27.224
Especially the living part.

00:27.225 --> 00:28.659
For you.

00:28.660 --> 00:30.628
No reason why you wouldn't keep on living.

00:30.629 --> 00:32.697
Your life.

00:32.698 --> 00:34.198
You know you're talking, right?

00:40.939 --> 00:48.929
♪ I can't believe
we're al-l-mo-o-st the-e-e-re ♪

00:55.887 --> 01:01.625
♪ I can't believe he's al-l-mo-o-st here ♪

01:01.626 --> 01:03.294
You're little Valencian princess

01:03.295 --> 01:05.129
