01:05.129 --> 01:07.665
He'll be here tonight as the sun has cast

01:07.666 --> 01:09.733
its last shadow upon the earth

01:09.734 --> 01:13.070
and the crescent moon is risen
above the Eastern Ridge.

01:13.071 --> 01:14.738
So, like 9:00?

01:15.840 --> 01:17.741
Yes, Gareth, he'll be here at 9:00.

01:17.742 --> 01:20.177
And I cannot wait!

01:20.178 --> 01:22.580
I will kill Galavant
in front of the queen,

01:22.581 --> 01:25.182
surprise her with the jewel,
and then finally bed

01:25.183 --> 01:27.751
the most delicate flower
in the seven realms.

01:27.752 --> 01:29.820
Attention, donkey turds!

01:29.821 --> 01:31.822
Where is that pox-ridden
sack of deformities

01:31.823 --> 01:33.157
known as my hand maiden?

01:33.158 --> 01:34.358
My hair is a disaster.

01:34.359 --> 01:36.427
Gwynne?

01:36.428 --> 01:37.528
My hair!

01:37.529 --> 01:39.063
Forgive me, My Queen.

01:40.865 --> 01:42.700
Was that too much to ask?

01:44.669 --> 01:47.037
Just think about it, hmm?

01:47.038 --> 01:50.474
We could, uh, we could do
a picnic, you know?

01:50.475 --> 01:51.875
Something super cazh.

01:51.876 --> 01:55.242
For the hundredth time, no.

01:55.244 --> 01:59.049
Your mouth is saying no, but I can see
your rotten teeth through that smile.

01:59.050 --> 02:00.289
Go on, you!

02:01.152 --> 02:03.053
She's going to be so surprised!

02:03.054 --> 02:05.289
No, she's not because you keep doing

02:05.290 --> 02:07.491
that stupid "evil king whisper" thing

02:07.492 --> 02:08.824
that everyone can hear.

02:08.826 --> 02:10.860
- How about this?
- Lower.

02:10.862 --> 02:12.462
- How about this?
- Oh, please.

02:12.463 --> 02:13.897
Oh, come on. That was good.

02:13.898 --> 02:15.799
For God's sakes, Gareth.
You're allowed to laugh.

02:15.800 --> 02:17.200
What are you two yabbering about?

02:17.201 --> 02:20.037
Nothing, darling. Nothing going on.

02:20.038 --> 02:22.806
That's right. There is nothing going on.

02:22.807 --> 02:25.175
I've been waiting for you
to find that jewel

02:25.176 --> 02:27.811
since we invaded this
wretched kingdom a year ago!

02:27.812 --> 02:31.148
Maddie, baby... chill.

02:31.149 --> 02:35.018
These things have a way
of... working themselves out.

02:35.019 --> 02:36.653
Why are you so calm?

02:36.654 --> 02:38.722
Normally when I yell at you,
you get tummy cramps

02:38.723 --> 02:40.857
and have to go poopy... your words.

02:40.858 --> 02:42.659
What can I say?

02:42.660 --> 02:46.029
I'm sleeping well, exercising,
laying off the wheat.

02:46.030 --> 02:48.064
Just in a really good place right now.

02:48.065 --> 02:50.200
You're inept.

02:50.201 --> 02:52.836
You're all inept!

02:52.837 --> 02:55.372
I can't even look at any of you anymore.

