you're rushing it.

05:33.681 --> 05:36.950
If you took the time to think about it...

05:36.951 --> 05:40.085
You smell. Really bad.

05:40.087 --> 05:43.023
Princess, I'm a knight of the seven realms

05:43.024 --> 05:44.624
