♪ And we're the Monks ♪

06:56.663 --> 06:58.331
♪ Hey, hey, we're the Monks ♪

06:58.332 --> 06:59.966
♪ Ooh wee-ahh ♪

06:59.967 --> 07:02.502
♪ Jazz hands ♪

07:02.503 --> 07:03.770
♪ Yeah! ♪

07:03.771 --> 07:06.039
Can't we just have a normal adventure?

07:08.108 --> 07:11.444
Is there anyone available
to counsel a person

07:11.445 --> 07:13.246
who might, through no fault of her own,

07:13.247 --> 07:15.815
be feeling guilty about a
fatal plot she's put into motion

07:15.816 --> 07:19.152
which could lead to the demise of someone
she's grown a little fond of?

07:20.320 --> 07:21.988
Just nod yes or no.

07:29.796 --> 07:31.864
Where are the kitchen trolls?

07:34.101 --> 07:35.001
Ah.

07:36.470 --> 07:38.371
Hey, m'lady.

07:38.372 --> 07:41.073
Who do I have to disembowel
around here to get a cup of tea?

07:41.074 --> 07:43.175
Oh, a thousand apologies.

07:43.176 --> 07:46.145
I was busy preparing
for tonight's celebration.

07:46.146 --> 07:47.446
Celebration for what?

07:47.447 --> 07:48.914
Oh, I... I wouldn't know.

07:48.915 --> 07:50.883
I-I'm just trying to stay alive,

07:50.884 --> 07:53.686
and I find it helps
not to ask too many questions.

07:58.925 --> 08:01.060
You're close with the king, aren't you?

08:01.061 --> 08:04.997
Eh, I wouldn't call us close,
but we hang, yeah.

08:05.932 --> 08:09.502
And, um, you fancy Gwynne, my hand maiden.

08:09.503 --> 08:11.303
Sha'!

08:11.304 --> 08:16.041
Listen, I know Richard's
keeping something from me.

08:16.042 --> 08:18.511
You find out what he has up his sleeve,

08:18.512 --> 08:22.715
and I will help you
get Gwynne into your bed.

08:22.716 --> 08:24.183
Ooh.

08:24.184 --> 08:26.118
A generous offer, My Queen,

08:26.119 --> 08:28.053
but I'm not even sure
we could both fit into my bed.

08:30.056 --> 08:31.390
You sleep in the kitchen?

08:31.391 --> 08:34.527
<i>Or...</i> Do I cook in my room?

08:34.528 --> 08:37.328
Why do I even talk to poor people?

08:37.330 --> 08:39.631
Do we have a deal?

08:39.633 --> 08:40.765
What the hell?

08:40.767 --> 08:43.068
I need all the help I can get.

08:43.068 --> 08:44.703
I sleep in a freaking kitchen.

08:44.704 --> 08:45.971
Okay.

08:45.972 --> 08:48.674
The king is having a secret meeting

08:48.675 --> 08:50.809
where I'm to serve snacks
and a light refreshment

08:50.810 --> 08:53.178
as soon as the croaks of the frogs

08:53.179 --> 08:55.080
usher in the raven's last call.

08:55.081 --> 08:56.815
So, like 9:00?

08:56.816 --> 08:58.350
Yeah, 9:00.

08:58.351 --> 08:59.651
Excellent.

08:59.652 --> 09:01.387
Take me there.

09:01.388 --> 09:03.389
Yes, m'lady.

09:03.390 --> 09:06.625
And King Richard said
if I didn't bring the jewel

09:06.626 --> 09:08.660
and Galavant back, he'd kill my parents.

09:08.661 --> 09:10.028
So, I lied to Galavant

09:10.029 --> 09:11.897
and told him
that the queen still loved him.

09:11.898 --> 09:13.999
He's walking into a trap of my own making!

09:14.000 --> 09:15.701
What can I do?

09:16.999 --> 09:18.968
Break your vow, or I break your pipe.

09:21.808 --> 09:24.810
- ♪ Bum ba-dum bum bum bum ♪
- So, uh...

09:24.811 --> 09:26.311
♪ Bum ba-dum bum bum ♪

09:26.312 --> 09:29.581
So, basically, you made a deal
with the evil king,

09:29.582 --> 09:31.917
but that was before you fell
for the handsome knight...

09:31.918 --> 09:34.019
Fell... fell for what? Fell for him?

09:34.020 --> 09:36.088
My child, if you argue,
I'm never gonna be able

09:36.089 --> 09:37.656
to make it back in time
for their big finish.

09:37.657 --> 09:39.291
But I need your advice.

09:39.292 --> 09:41.059
I'm supposed to bring Galavant to the king

09:41.060 --> 09:43.895
when the barking of the hounds
wakens the fairies in the evening

09:43.896 --> 09:45.797
so that they may begin
their nocturnal dance.

09:45.798 --> 09:47.966
So, like 9:00?

09:47.967 --> 09:50.369
Yeah. 9:00.

09:52.572 --> 09:56.842
It's 9:03. Why am I the only one
who's ever on time?

09:58.344 --> 10:00.746
There should be a standardized system

10:00.747 --> 10:03.281
based on the rotation of the earth

10:03.282 --> 10:06.418
in relation to its position
to the sun and the moon.

10:06.419 --> 10:08.653
You sound like a witch.

10:08.654 --> 10:11.890
Regardless, it is very rude of Galavant

10:11.891 --> 10:13.892
to be late to his own killing.

10:13.893 --> 10:15.861
Galavant's coming?

10:15.862 --> 10:17.829
The king didn't give me a head count.

10:17.830 --> 10:19.998
Oh, I came up with the most <i> perfect</i> line

10:19.999 --> 10:21.600
for when I first see him.

10:21.601 --> 10:24.069
In my most intimidating voice,
I'm going to say,

10:24.070 --> 10:27.472
"Well, well, well"...

10:27.473 --> 10:29.040
Nope. I'm gonna save it.

10:30.076 --> 10:31.242
Oh. Here we go.

10:33.746 --> 10:36.014
Well, well...

10:37.183 --> 10:39.651
- Where the hell's Galavant?
- There's been a change in plans.

10:39.652 --> 10:42.787
You'll get the jewel
and set my parents free,

10:42.788 --> 10:44.255
but Galavant stays alive.

10:44.256 --> 10:46.157
I see.

10:46.158 --> 10:48.193
How utterly predictable.

10:48.194 --> 10:51.362
The princess has fallen
for the noble knight.

10:51.363 --> 10:53.264
Of course she has.

10:53.265 --> 10:55.233
I can't let a guy like that live.

10:55.234 --> 10:56.601
Well, then the deal is off.

10:56.602 --> 10:58.203
You'll never see the jewel again.

10:58.204 --> 11:01.139
You're adorable.

11:01.140 --> 11:02.574
No, my darling.

11:02.575 --> 11:05.343
You see, you will bring me Galavant

11:05.344 --> 11:10.086
<i>and</i> the jewel or else
you'll suffer the same fate...

11:10.088 --> 11:12.150
As your parents!

11:13.386 --> 11:16.422
- It's all right, honey.
- We're alive.

11:16.422 --> 11:17.344
What?!

11:17.346 --> 11:19.724
The king convinced us it would be funny.

11:19.725 --> 11:21.993
We've been prisoners a long time.

11:21.994 --> 11:23.494
We lost perspective.

11:23.495 --> 11:26.631
You should have seen your face!

11:26.632 --> 11:27.999
You were like, "aah!"

11:29.201 --> 11:30.334
"Ooh!"

11:30.335 --> 11:31.969
Oh, but make no mistake.

11:31.970 --> 11:33.838
If you don't bring me Galavant,
I will kill them.

11:35.140 --> 11:36.674
For realsies.

11:39.491 --> 11:43.558
♪ And we're the Monks,
hey, hey, we're the Monks ♪

11:43.560 --> 11:46.293
♪ Yeah ♪

11:46.295 --> 11:47.562
What's happening?

11:47.563 --> 11:48.897
I'll tell you what's happening.

11:48.898 --> 11:50.342
Our Sid sings like a freaking angel.

11:50.333 --> 11:52.467
No, this plan, this whole thing.

11:52.468 --> 11:55.337
- How did it come to this?
- Princess, relax.

11:55.338 --> 11:56.872
It's gonna go great.

11:56.873 --> 11:59.875
They already expect these guys
to perform at the castle.

11:59.876 --> 12:01.438
We're just gonna sneak in with them

12:01.440 --> 12:03.441
and infiltrate from the inside.

12:05.715 --> 12:07.716
Turns out you were right.

12:07.717 --> 12:09.851
As usual, I needed a better plan.

12:09.852 --> 12:11.186
Galavant...

12:11.187 --> 12:13.154
I'm only magnanimous once every 10 years,

12:13.155 --> 12:14.789
so just let this happen.

12:14.790 --> 12:17.759
You saw the best in me and...

12:17.760 --> 12:21.852
Ultimately reminded me what
it means to be a real knight.

12:22.031 --> 12:23.098
And here we are.

12:23.099 --> 12:25.567
So, thank you...

12:25.568 --> 12:29.838
For bringing me back to me.

12:29.839 --> 12:33.975
Against all the odds, it's, um...

12:33.976 --> 12:36.878
Well, it's been a pleasure.

12:36.879 --> 12:40.982
You really don't
have to thank me for anything.

12:40.983 --> 12:45.153
You actually have
a lot of nice qualities...

12:45.154 --> 12:46.388
All on your own.

12:47.189 --> 12:48.857
Careful, princess.

12:48.858 --> 12:50.859
You're getting dangerously close
to paying me a compliment.

12:50.860 --> 12:53.361
I can do compliments.

12:53.362 --> 12:56.331
I mean, you know your way around a horse,

12:56.332 --> 12:59.400
you're not so bad with a sword,

12:59.401 --> 13:02.470
and your beard magically stays
the same length all the time.

13:04.006 --> 13:09.077
And... you have an ability to see
the best in people

13:09.078 --> 13:11.513
even after they've wronged you.

13:13.582 --> 13:16.417
Like with Madalena.

13:16.418 --> 13:18.119
Right.

13:18.120 --> 13:19.787
Madalena.

13:19.788 --> 13:24.092
Oh, man, this robe
is really itching my junk.

13:24.093 --> 13:26.661
Oh, you left your clothes on underneath.

13:26.662 --> 13:27.829
Right.

