13:43.579 --> 13:46.114
and what seems like the amount
of exclamation points,

13:46.115 --> 13:47.949
it's a little hard to tell.

13:47.950 --> 13:49.717
This is the writing of a happy queen

13:49.718 --> 13:53.121
